---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { CONTACT_EMAIL } from '../consts';
---

<Layout
  title="Case Studies"
  description="Real-world engagements from RePass Cloud covering Microsoft 365 identity automation, finance workflow automation, and multi-cloud FinOps tooling."
>

  <!-- Page header -->
  <div style="background:var(--rpc-surface); border-bottom:1px solid var(--rpc-border); padding: 3rem 0 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label">Real-world work</div>
      <h1 style="font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2rem); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Case Studies</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--rpc-muted); font-size:1rem; max-width:560px; margin:0;">
        Documented engagements showing the breadth and depth of what we build. Enterprise identity
        automation, finance workflows, and multi-cloud cost governance at scale.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Case studies -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:900px;">
      <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2rem;">

        <!-- Case Study 1 -->
        <div class="aethon-card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--rpc-primary);">
          <div class="section-label">Case Study · Enterprise / Retail (multi-brand)</div>
          <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Microsoft 365 Identity &amp; Access Automation</h2>

          <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Problem</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                Manual daily IT management of Microsoft 365 access for approximately 2,100 employees
                across multiple retail brands in Australia and New Zealand. Distribution lists, shared
                mailbox access, licence assignments, and group memberships all required daily manual
                intervention by IT staff.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Solution</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                Fully automated, rule-driven scheduling system with time-aware access control,
                ownership-based approvals, and full audit logging. Eliminated all manual IT
                intervention for day-to-day identity and access operations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Outcome</div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid);"></i>
              <span style="font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:600;">Zero daily manual IT intervention for access management</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Microsoft 365</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Identity Automation</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">PowerShell</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Entra ID</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 2 -->
        <div class="aethon-card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--rpc-primary);">
          <div class="section-label">Case Study · Multi-brand Retail / Franchise</div>
          <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Finance Workflow Automation — Petty Cash</h2>

          <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Problem</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                4 FTE accounts payable staff manually processing petty cash daily across 200+ brands
                and 2,000+ locations across Australia, New Zealand, and Singapore. Manual reconciliation,
                access provisioning, and approval routing consumed significant operational capacity.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Solution</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                End-to-end finance workflow automation integrated with Active Directory, Entra ID,
                and Oracle HCM. Automated access provisioning, approval routing, reconciliation, and
                reporting across all brands and regions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Outcome</div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid);"></i>
              <span style="font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:600;">Eliminated manual petty cash processing for 4 FTE accounts payable staff</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Business Process Automation</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Entra ID</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Active Directory</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Oracle HCM</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Case Study 3 -->
        <div class="aethon-card" style="border-left: 4px solid var(--rpc-primary);">
          <div class="section-label">Case Study · Enterprise Technology (~5,000 employees, global)</div>
          <h2 style="font-size:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1rem;">Multi-Cloud FinOps Tooling</h2>

          <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.5rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem;">
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Problem</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                Approximately $7M USD per year in cloud spend across AWS, Azure, and GCP with no
                unified spend visibility. Cloud costs could not be classified by workload, team, or
                initiative. No mechanism to track savings decisions from identification through to
                realisation.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Solution</div>
              <p style="font-size:0.9rem; color:var(--rpc-text); line-height:1.65; margin:0;">
                Multi-cloud cost analysis and governance platform: classifies spend, produces
                evidence-backed findings, manages decision lifecycle, and tracks realised savings
                across all three cloud providers from a single interface.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
            <div style="font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:600; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.06em; color:var(--rpc-muted); margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Outcome</div>
            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:0.5rem;">
              <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill" style="color:var(--rpc-valid);"></i>
              <span style="font-size:0.9rem; font-weight:600;">Unified cost visibility and savings realisation tracking across $7M USD/year cloud estate</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">FinOps</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">Multi-Cloud Governance</span>
            <span class="badge badge-primary">AWS</span>
            <span class="badge badge-primary">Azure</span>
            <span class="badge badge-secondary">GCP</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-label" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">Work with us</div>
      <h2>Have a similar challenge?</h2>
      <p>
        Tell us about your environment and what you're trying to solve. We work with organisations
        that need enterprise software or automation built properly.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
          Get in touch <i class="bi bi-arrow-right"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
